defaultMaternity leave and childcare
default5
default. The years spent working to secure academic independence and a permanent position are also the years many people choose to
default ‘settle down’ and/or
default start a family. A number of factors seem to influence whether this decision will 
defaultbe seen as suited to
default an acad
defaultemic career. During a workshop at Imperial College London (in association with the Imperial College Science Comm
