default“salaries in academic postdocs aren’t enough to support a family”. One of the women was looking to leave academia for this 
defaultreason;
default another told us
default that childcare
default “will cost about 70% of my post-tax salary. Certainly, if I had another child, I would have to either give up work or move to a more highly paid job
default”
default. The group observed that many of the male postdocs with children they knew had partners who earned more. 
